{"tid":1739753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［集氣tvb] 朋友話留呢段會比tvb FB block","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:36:23.000Z","uid":42487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88a6a9be86abd1d313094045dd30d2017e95a13a","tid":1739753,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"話說我fd 見今日tvb 台慶<br />\n就嚮佢fb 賀賀佢，人地祝佢執笠都無事<br />\n但佢留左幾次呢段就比tvb block 9左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1991年9月，袁志偉在六四事件後獨家訪問時任中國國務院總理李鵬，而且笑容滿面地與後者親切握手，為香港新聞歷史上的一個經典場面。<br />\n<br />\n這個專訪卻累及無綫電視在該段時間的收視暴跌，更被部分香港市民稱呼為「走狗台」。<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月<br />\nTvb新聞部袁志偉令tvb 壽終正寢<br />\n</span></span><br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/袁志偉_(記者\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E8%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89_%28%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=b7675ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/袁志偉_(記者</a>)<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們不如一齊試下睇下佢block唔block得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sAMRUY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsAMRUY8.png&h=87cc4264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f5af0e5b918200f9e6a4d19a7c551daba99d0b9","tid":1739753,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:49:30.000Z","msg":"娛樂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"9440c5f40da4c91c0f9e53cb798072de55da40b9","tid":1739753,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"娛樂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2"},{"pid":"755dcc6985cb5c52fe73da345f432441fb4614f3","tid":1739753,"uid":281968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl